                'content' => "Content marketing is about creating valuable, relevant content that attracts and engages your target audience. Here's how to develop a winning strategy:\n\n**Foundation: Know Your Audience**\n\n1. **Create Buyer Personas**\n   - Demographics and psychographics\n   - Pain points and challenges\n   - Goals and aspirations\n   - Preferred content formats\n\n2. **Map the Customer Journey**\n   - Awareness stage content\n   - Consideration stage content\n   - Decision stage content\n   - Retention and advocacy content\n\n**Content Planning:**\n\n• **Content Audit**\n  - Analyze existing content performance\n  - Identify content gaps\n  - Repurpose high-performing content\n\n• **Editorial Calendar**\n  - Plan content themes by month\n  - Balance educational and promotional content\n  - Align with business goals and seasons\n\n• **Content Mix (80/20 Rule)**\n  - 80% valuable, educational content\n  - 20% promotional content\n\n**Content Types That Work:**\n\n1. **Educational Content**\n   - How-to guides and tutorials\n   - Industry insights and trends\n   - Tips and best practices\n\n2. **Social Proof**\n   - Customer success stories\n   - Case studies\n   - User-generated content\n\n3. **Behind-the-Scenes**\n   - Company culture content\n   - Process explanations\n   - Team spotlights\n\n**Distribution Strategy:**\n\n• **Owned Media**\n  - Your website and blog\n  - Email newsletters\n  - Podcasts or video channels\n\n• **Earned Media**\n  - Guest posting\n  - Podcast appearances\n  - Media coverage\n\n• **Paid Media**\n  - Social media advertising\n  - Content promotion\n  - Influencer partnerships\n\n**Measuring Success:**\n- Traffic and engagement metrics\n- Lead generation and conversion rates\n- Brand awareness and sentiment\n- Customer lifetime value\n\n**Content Creation Tips:**\n- Start with one format and master it\n- Repurpose content across multiple channels\n- Use storytelling to make content memorable\n- Include clear calls-to-action\n- Optimize for search engines\n\nConsistency beats perfection. Start creating valuable content regularly, and refine your strategy based on what resonates with your audience.",
